{"tid":1072160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[mola mola]翻車魚沖上澳洲海灘 漁民︰初時以為是沉船殘骸","createTime":"2019-03-22T00:21:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T00:00:36.000Z","uid":47674,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"441ea6c94829bef28befcb87f14debd9fd3e504b","tid":1072160,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T00:21:22.000Z","msg":"mola mola<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【稀客現身】翻車魚沖上澳洲海灘 漁民︰初時以為是沉船殘骸<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190322&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59392996\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190322%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59392996&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE2Abrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=07ea912b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190322%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59392996&h=5d661c79\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190322&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59392996</a><br />\n<br />\n澳洲南部一個沙灘發現翻車魚屍體，有漁民說過去從沒見過真的翻車魚，起初發現牠時甚至以為是沉船殘骸。<br />\n<br />\n格熱拉克（Linette Grzelak）拍下翻車魚屍體相片，再上載至社交網facebook，「我不相信這是真的，直至我上網搜尋翻車魚的資料才知道」。她的伴侶瓊斯（Steven Jones）從事捕漁多年，起初發現牠時以為是一塊沉船殘骸，「他知道這是甚麼，但現實生活中沒有見過」，他們又形容翻車魚非常沉重，皮膚粗糙得像犀牛一樣。報道指，翻車魚屍體其後相信被沖回海中。<br />\n<br />\n這條翻車魚屍體在庫龍國家公園（Coorong&nbsp;National Park）被發現，南澳洲博物館魚類藏品經理福斯特(Ralph Foster)表示，該區甚少見到翻車魚出沒，牠身長1.8米，屬中等體型，「我想很多人都以為牠是假的」。<br />\n<br />\n翻車魚是全球最重的硬骨魚類，大多在溫帶海洋中找到，牠可以長至4米、重達2500公斤。翻車魚對人類沒有害，但游近岸時會被誤以為是鯊魚，若與船隻相撞也可能會撞翻船隻。"},{"pid":"4d952f6bbb573dc443b05d16d1e42dd9d496a302","tid":1072160,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T00:25:53.000Z","msg":"翻車魚翻車了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c121be74fc20a611aed4b9534a49244cb38ddf8e","tid":1072160,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T00:25:58.000Z","msg":"好大舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"febfb72e0d7b055c4e382730c7cd3741b14208d0","tid":1072160,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T00:26:23.000Z","msg":"Molamola<strong></strong>"},{"pid":"16dbc0740276cdfd21cd27b51ea261ffa41df95d","tid":1072160,"uid":61882,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T00:40:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://speeder117.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/screenshot3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fspeeder117.files.wordpress.com%2F2015%2F01%2Fscreenshot3.png&h=ff6c817b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMola mola<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f04c7cfd0da8e64065b254e78625243a498c68","tid":1072160,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16dbc0740276cdfd21cd27b51ea261ffa41df95d","tid":1072160,"uid":61882,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T00:40:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://speeder117.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/screenshot3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fspeeder117.files.wordpress.com%2F2015%2F01%2Fscreenshot3.png&h=ff6c817b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMola mola<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T00:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3cac3307aa755189be18c7571831f54a5cce2a9","tid":1072160,"uid":6122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:49:33.000Z","msg":"新加坡"},{"pid":"d39d3925ed3dd5eca35866d06d328802a2ec300d","tid":1072160,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T05:48:21.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"086c635fb1dd328